{"tid":972310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人屌大陸人黎自由行，但自己又成日去日本玩！","createTime":"2019-01-07T09:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T11:31:10.000Z","uid":162303,"like":26,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3d160bbf91378f5f2c3d636bc7fe58490283857f","tid":972310,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"香港人去日本貪咩？<br />\n機票平，坐飛機去好快好方便，<br />\n日本野高質食物安全，地方乾淨<br />\nYen平，港元兌抵玩！<br />\n<br />\n咁調返轉頭講一樣，大陸人黎香港自由行咪一樣！<br />\n貪交通方便，坐高鐵又24小時通關，<br />\n車費平可以即日來回<br />\n人民幣強，兌8算<br />\n香港貨夠真，香港品牌，香港製造<br />\n<br />\n咁分析完，唔難怪咁多大陸人到港！<br />\n唔該本土派屌人之前問下自己先！<br />\n<br />\n利申，靠自由行開飯有既得利益關係"},{"pid":"01fe30af32fddfa39dab80c4128db297abdf7c73","tid":972310,"uid":133896,"like":18,"dislike":19,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"香港人係咁架喇?第1日黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4c69471e43b8dbf4ac29445a97cf69b0035ecb","tid":972310,"uid":60545,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"日本啲舖租有冇因為香港人而升高？有冇令到日本物價升先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9ad17dcb710315e78fad4a21cf7dc48673e650","tid":972310,"uid":76793,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:59:25.000Z","msg":"2睇啦<br />\n不過講自律 大陸人一定仆街過港人<br />\n<br />\n雖然成日都見到港人係日本點仆街<br />\n但一定無大陸人咁撚多<br />\n<br />\n起碼唔會周街痾屎尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c552d11e76411ea27dab3de83223bd9286e9413","tid":972310,"uid":152476,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"香港人無講「要不是我們，日本完蛋了」"},{"pid":"af132300ba9d2b771832a0337ccce7c204c741be","tid":972310,"uid":152476,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"fb4c69471e43b8dbf4ac29445a97cf69b0035ecb","tid":972310,"uid":60545,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"日本啲舖租有冇因為香港人而升高？有冇令到日本物價升先？<img src=